product.title: Lambert - The Thomas Vegan Leather Wallet in Black
product.body_html: Exclusive collaboration. The THOMAS is the first Lambert men wallet designed in collaboration with Frank and Oak. It has the ideal size to carry all your essentials. With its minimalist and neat appearance, it's the timeless style that'll always have your back.
